{"tid":2350013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"因為愛佢所以放手","createTime":"2021-01-02T04:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T10:22:28.000Z","uid":305961,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9418fdd3fd73152d754087f955abb657ce283c2","tid":2350013,"uid":305961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"我同條女同一間中學，一齊左接近3個月<br />\n一直以黎都好sweet冇乜點鬧過交<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過早幾日<br />\n我本身同條女仲好sweet <br />\n點知前日佢冇啦啦同我講分手<br />\n因為佢屋企人想佢考好啲公開試所以唔俾佢拍拖<br />\n佢同屋企人嘈左好耐最尾都係聽屋企人講分手<br />\n佢依然愛我 我都愛佢<br />\n不過佢更加聽屋企人嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇綠帽<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打c打<br />\n我應該要點做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡力挽留佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為愛佢所以放手"},{"pid":"b14e66920f1e9020bf7cc2b959f05a789d1a6345","tid":2350013,"uid":122401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"咁咪考完先一齊-.-"},{"pid":"e6a16924d02402ebf6e9bb6c942e93b83dffc369","tid":2350013,"uid":316014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"你自己諗會唔會後悔啦&hellip;<br />\n我就覺得兩個人相愛好難得，外來因素搞到分手真係唔得。<br />\n再講，考完試之後一齊返嘅機會大唔大？<br />\n博唔博？<br />\n雖然唔係想難為對方，但唔想後悔就試吓諗辦法，睇吓可唔可以再傾吓搵返個平衡點。<br />\n最緊要唔好後悔呀。"},{"pid":"221a4510a28ed9464f1a1c78496da6ae4d4da640","tid":2350013,"uid":323845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89668ed8ab27d67dc9626b954b9707e968d0c2e","tid":2350013,"uid":305961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b14e66920f1e9020bf7cc2b959f05a789d1a6345","tid":2350013,"uid":122401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"咁咪考完先一齊-.-"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"佢叫我唔好等佢<br />\n佢話唔知幾時屋企人先再俾拍拖"},{"pid":"703815a1cd320c366ae3110dce270af12bd92793","tid":2350013,"uid":3059